Greenpoint Avenue, st, and adjoining the N.W. corner of Gale Avenue. The three-story building is the Engine 259 and Hook and Ladder 128 fire house of the New York City Fire Department. A portion of Public School 80 is on the left.

November 1, 1936

P. L. Sperr
